SA's TV and showbiz darling Minnie Dlamini got the shock of her life when thugs pounced on her. Sunday World learnt this week that the adored presenter and model was robbed of her wedding ring in May last year, a month before she jetted off to Russia where she was one of the presenters for SuperSport during the Fifa World Cup. TO READ MORE ON THIS STORY GET A COPY OF TODAY'S SUNDAY WORLD.